  <inline-graphic xlink:href="pntd.0003398.e226.jpg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
 </inline-formula> of transmission, see 
 <xref rid="pntd.0003398-Stein1" ref-type="bibr">[45]</xref>, 
 <xref rid="pntd.0003398-LloydSmith1" ref-type="bibr">[46]</xref>). To this end, for different values of the contribution of human-to-human transmission, 
 <inline-formula>
  <inline-graphic xlink:href="pntd.0003398.e227.jpg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
 </inline-formula>, we calculated i) the proportion of cases when 
 <inline-formula>
